{"tid":749771,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[LOL] Deer代表香港出席「電子競技研討會」","createTime":"2018-07-20T09:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T12:44:44.000Z","uid":92459,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4f70ac23c73239af828f31c72d414f8d36b07d","tid":749771,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"【港電競之光】<br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會將在7月21日於瑞士洛桑奧林匹克博物館，舉行「電子競技研討會」，旨在討論電子競技會否有機會納入奧運項目，將有包括選手、戰隊、媒體、贊助商和賽事組織等出席。<br />\n<br />\n香港唯一代表，由環球電競旗下的女子電子競技職業戰隊 PandaCute 隊長陳嘉靖 (Deer)代表出席，並將於研討會上發言，向國際奧委會講述目前香港電子競技業的概況、選手待遇與及女子職業選手的發展。<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇咩想幫DEER大家反應？<br />\n<br />\nPandaCute 電競職業戰隊<br />\n<br />\n#EWeSports #香港電競代表喺奧委會發言 #PDQ #DEER #香港電競之光 #大家係要支持 #你又點估到打機可以打到同國際奧委會講數<br />\n<br />\n來源<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/175013_8e1d9b7c546278946c8221ae4f3cf7a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F175013_8e1d9b7c546278946c8221ae4f3cf7a1.jpg&h=a2e47885&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca7875b4516abf198834f5b4bef3c48f0da81a09","tid":749771,"uid":92459,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"大家覺得有冇代表性"},{"pid":"332cb03de2ffda2ae909d453189a22d25eaf3658","tid":749771,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61009a428b1d8482833a405919b49daf232b8708","tid":749771,"uid":8867,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:54:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f72abf49ff5f24b40f6785dfcd688db6cb6b1640","tid":749771,"uid":25367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:54:51.000Z","msg":"何德何能"},{"pid":"d45183ef8e86b15400fe03f5f82f69ffa8a4ab6a","tid":749771,"uid":92459,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"61009a428b1d8482833a405919b49daf232b8708","tid":749771,"uid":8